<div class="mdui-typo"><h1 id="discourage-vt">discourage <strong><em>vt</em></strong></h1>
<p>英 /dɪs'kʌrɪdʒ/    美 /dɪs'kɜːrɪdʒ/  </p>
<h2 id="_1">释义</h2>
<h4 id="1">1.★ <strong>使泄气；使沮丧； 劝阻：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>Do not let any failure discourage you, for you can never tell how close you may be to victory. 
不要因任何失败而灰心，因为你永远不清楚自己离成功可能有多近。</p><footer>2013 湖南改</footer></div>

<ul>
<li>discourage sb from doing sth:</li>
</ul>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>We discourage you from smoking except in specific areas. 
除特定区域外，我们禁止吸烟。</p><footer>外研⑧ – 2</footer></div>

<h2 id="_2">派生词汇</h2>
<p>discouraged /dɪs'kʌrɪdʒd/ adj <br />
discouraging /dɪs'kʌrɪdʒɪŋ/ adj   </p></div>